    "col_intro_title": "What is this site about",
    "col_intro_text": "In this site, I'm presenting some of my current interests on what to pursue in my life. The motivation is to gain feedback, reach possible collaborators and to fing funding/employment avenus. \n\nAdditionally, \nDepending on how they are written, some plans for texts can also act as drafts for the text and can be continuously improved until they can be published as finalized texts. Having the plans/drafts public makes me more motivated to focus on them at that stage, since I know they can be seen and have an impact at that already. This increased focus increases the probability that the plans/drafts will become final texts at some points. \n\nMy possible interests are not limited to the ones presented here, but I hope they  also express my interests in general. \n\n------\nThe site has been vibecoded with Claude. ",
    "details_title": "Descriptions",
    "details_hint": "Click on a topic in the graph to show its description below",
    "vote_title": "Influence my focus",
    "vote_text": "What themes, projects or skill you would like me to pursue? You can choose here: \n\nI'll take your opinions into account. \n\nForm also has field to give hints on possible collaborators or funding sources. ",
    "funding_title": "Funding/work opportunities",
    "funding_intro": "Currently I'm pursuing these interests on my own time but I'm also looking for work . Feel free to contact me with suggestions on regarding work on these intererests or anything else you think I might be interested in. \n\nHere is my current preference order for different funding sources:",
